sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Shield as 🛡️ Pre-Payment Shield
    participant React as ⚛️ React Frontend
    participant Firebase as 🔥 Firestore
    participant Flask as 🐍 Flask ML API
    participant RF as 🤖 Random Forest

    User->>React: Enter UPI + Amount
    React->>Shield: Run 6-factor check
    Shield->>Shield: Levenshtein spoof check
    Shield->>Shield: Amount Z-score
    Shield->>Shield: Time of day risk
    Shield-->>React: Verdict (ALLOW / CAUTION / BLOCK)

    alt Verdict is ALLOW or CAUTION
        User->>React: Confirm payment
        React->>Flask: POST /predict {features}
        Flask->>RF: Score transaction
        RF-->>Flask: fraud_probability
        Flask-->>React: {verdict, score, explanation}

        alt Score < 0.4 (SAFE)
            React->>Firebase: Write transaction {fraudVerdict: SAFE}
            Firebase-->>React: Transaction saved
            React-->>User: ✅ Payment successful
        else Score 0.4–0.7 (MEDIUM)
            React-->>User: ⚠️ Warning shown, user confirms
            React->>Firebase: Write transaction {fraudVerdict: MEDIUM_RISK}
        else Score > 0.7 (HIGH RISK)
            React-->>User: 🚨 Payment blocked
            React->>Firebase: Write alert notification
            Firebase-->>User: Push notification sent
        end
    else Verdict is BLOCK
        React-->>User: 🚨 Blocked before sending
    end

    React->>Flask: POST /explain-transaction
    Flask-->>React: SHAP factor breakdown
    React-->>User: Show anomaly explanation
